# OpenClaw Starter Agent

An open-source local AI assistant that brings AI co-worker capabilities to developers.

## Description

OpenClaw is a powerful local AI assistant that runs entirely on your machine, keeping your data private while providing:

- **Persistent Memory** - Remembers your preferences and past interactions across sessions
- **Skill System** - Custom skill system for extensibility
- **Deep System Integration** - File system, shell commands, browser automation, Git operations
- **Feishu Integration** - Native integration with 飞书 for Chinese users

## Use Cases

- Code generation and debugging
- Workflow automation
- File processing and data analysis
- Browser automation
- Feishu messaging and calendar management

## Tech Stack

- TypeScript/Node.js
- Multiple AI provider support (OpenAI, Anthropic, Google, etc.)

## Getting Started

```bash
# Install
npm install -g openclaw

# Initialize
openclaw init

# Start
openclaw start
```

